additional_data.description: The spirit of a blade with miraculous sharpness. A slice from her can cut through anything. She constantly requests duels with other sword spirits so that she can improve her skills. She hopes her time put into self-improvement will one day allow her to stand alongside the other Five Great Swords. In terms of her sharpness, she is equal or superior to any other sword. But what she really needs might not be sharpness at all...
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Thanksgiving Day Beatdown" Event: Clear Chapter 3
◦ "Thanksgiving Day Beatdown" Event: Exchange for 1000 Seed of Thanks
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slighty increases the drop rate of Seed of Thanks during the "Thanksgiving Day Beatdown" event.

main: "This blade brings honor to the Goto name!"
skill: "I can cut through anything, even my own name!"
limit_break: "Hm... Coming with you was the right choice after all."
